{"tid":1408502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我有必勝法]唯一方法令有壓力既公務員以及所有打工仔可以輕鬆罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T22:34:50.000Z","uid":180561,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7665adbd35e68c06e45dcbe10aefbb77997e65","tid":1408502,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有好多好多打工仔都係黃底, 但係上面太大壓力</span></span>. 唔好再講今日唔罷, 香港冇明日. <br />\n我既必勝法:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堵塞所有主要幹道</span></span><br />\n包括 「屯門公路 吐露港公路 龍翔道 紅隧 西隧」<br />\n搞地鐵咁多巴絲都輕鬆處理過, 人手各自分配, 各自爬山, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係馬路都要人</span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n佢地朝早坐巴士又塞, 地鐵又塞, 唔通行返工????<br />\n佢地需要一個<span style=\"color: red;\">冇得輸既理由</span>被迫罷工, 就係<span style=\"color: red;\">連巴士都冇得坐</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">各位如果覺得以上有道理, 請睇埋下面</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔會等人幫我塞馬路</span>, 我聽朝會早D起身帶多件衫, 戴埋頂帽, 變個身就出去堵路. 盡地一煲. 平時坐巴士既咁多位, 試下早D出門, 如果上到車 條路暢通, 多謝你, 呢個時候可以係大馬路落車進行堵路. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我愛香港, <br />\n香港人上</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce3423e5b59e0580fceece80ab8d0ab401bb07a2","tid":1408502,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"87cecf32b51c8e3f0da6a5b07546fd8f15b06fe8","tid":1408502,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"07947d8d04c462356f91a98579ec2b8d30d2e7eb","tid":1408502,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T